719831f-a.folder: Fort Washington Aven & 181st Street (West), Manhattan, NY
719831f-a.text:
Fort Washington Avenue, at the northwest corner of West 181st St. These views show the twin houses that were owned by Ward and Hyatt in the 1876's. They are the same architectural design built by
De Long.
E. P. Chrystie  1923
